## Marketing Q3 QBR

[QBR Sharepoint](https://share.amazon.com/sites/amazon-business-marketing/SitePages/Home.aspx?RootFolder=%2Fsites%2Famazon%2Dbusiness%2Dmarketing%2FShared%20Documents%2FQBRs%2F2024%20QBRs%2FQ3%2724&FolderCTID=0x0120001FB22FCF2CF7924CB51C27FCDD2F7420&View=%7BF3C5E47D%2D158E%2D44A2%2D896B%2DC239A354FA8E%7D)

_FAQ_
**What traffic drivers are successful in the consumer playbook that AB has yet to adopt? [Affiliate, FreeSearch, ADA]**

Associates has been running as HOTW since 2021, bringing in 5.4k registrations annually. Associates has been extremely efficient due to it’s bounty/pay-for-performance model, driving 33% iE%CCP YTD. Current performance is derived through Amazon Consumer affiliates, joining to support retail activities, and electing to participate in the Amazon Business program secondarily. The channel is largely unsaturated due to high resource requirements needed to expand the program focusing on B2B, and fraud monitoring. We see Associates as an opportunity to expand new customer acquisition and drive current customers back to AB. We are scoping this opportunity with proposal ETA EO Jan. 

